<TEXT>
STRUGGLING to maintain earnings in the face of falling aluminium prices,
Australia's Comalco has increased sackings and cutbacks at its huge Boyne
Island smelter on the central Queensland coast.
Comalco also has deferred a ADollars 1bn (Dollars 780m) expansion of its
